content: Prof. Raul Vicente – Natural and Artificial Intelligence Lab Prof. Raul Vicente Yet another physicist turned into neuroscientist. After 7 years at the Max-Planck Institute for Brain Research, where he tried to learn some biology, he moved to Tartu to learn the other side of the story – the computational perspective. Email: raulvicente@gmail.com Abstraction, geometric data analysis, complex systems
